== Overview ==
The Titan Deflector significantly increases shield effectiveness by dynamically changing the angle of the shield projector to match incoming fire.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Titan Deflector can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
